\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 48. V. dillenii} Crantz,{\i  Stirp. Austr.} ed. 2,{\b  2}: 352 (1769). Like {\b 47} but up to 20 cm and more robust; corolla 4-5 mm in diameter, deep blue; style c. 1·5 mm; seeds c. 1·25 × 1 mm. 2n = 16.{\i  Dry places. E. & E.C. Europe, northwards to the Baltic region, and extending locally westwards to N.E. Spain.} Au Cz Ga Ge Gr He Hs Hu It Ju Po Rm Rs (?B, C, W, K, E).
